Abencat Browser (阿笨猫指纹浏览器)
=================================

This software is an open-source controller / launcher for a fingerprint browser.

Fingerprint kernel attribution
------------------------------
The actual anti-detection browser engine is **CloakBrowser**, © CloakHQ:

    https://github.com/CloakHQ/CloakBrowser

CloakBrowser is a stealth Chromium build with source-level fingerprint patches
(Canvas / WebGL / Audio / Fonts / WebRTC, etc.). Abencat Browser launches this
kernel with `--fingerprint-*` flags and provides profile management, a local
automation API, an MCP server, a proxy pool, encryption and a UI.

The CloakBrowser kernel is **NOT** redistributed in this repository. It is
downloaded from the official CloakBrowser releases at setup time via
`scripts/download-browser.{sh,ps1}`. All rights to the browser engine belong to
CloakHQ and are governed by CloakBrowser's own license/terms.

